detail.name: Mecha Frieza
detail.effect: [Blocker] (After an opponent's attack, you may switch this card to Rest Mode and change the target of the attack to this card.)[When KO'd] Look at 3 cards from the top of your deck, reveal up to 1 card with 《Frieza Clan》 in its special traits and add it to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order.
